      <h1 class="page-heading">Medical Cannabis Has Been Used For Over 1,000 Years.</h1>
<div class="default-home-bg">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row home-container">
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <div class="home-links-container">
          <a href="/ailments">Learn</a>
        </div>
        <p>Cannabis is 100% non-toxic and has been used as medicine throughout the ages.</p>
        <p>Learn how medical cannabis has been used in treating 60+ ailments. </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <div class="ailments">
          <ul class="ailments">
            <% Ailment.home_ailments.each do |ailment| %>
            <li>
              <a href="<%= ailment_path(ailment) %>" class="ailment-name"><%= ailment.name %></a>
            </li>
            <% end %>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row home-container">
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <div class="home-links-container">
          <a href="/reviews/new">Journal</a>
        </div>
        <p>Research has proven that journaling oneâ€™s diet and exercise has increased health benefits.  Journaling your medical cannabis product experiences is no different.</p>
        <p>Journal experiences in 10 seconds - members use their journals to better understand dosage and effectiveness of medical cannabis products while also recalling their favorites quickly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag 'review_example.png' %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row home-container">
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <div class="home-links-container">
          <a href="/products">Discover</a>
        </div>
        <p>With thousands of medical cannabis products available, finding the most effective for your ailment can be time consuming and expensive.</p>
        <p>Discover favorite products members use for treating specific ailments. </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <% Product.limit(6).each do |product| %>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="panel panel-default product">
              <div class="panel-body">
                <h4><%= link_to product.name, product  %></h4>
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-md-8">
                    <%= select_tag :effectiveness, options_for_select(EFFECTIVENESS_RATINGS, product.avg_rating), class: 'rating' %>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="product-category-icon <%= product.category %>"><%= product.category[0].capitalize %></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="spacer"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>




